-- Erdogan Urges Banks to Lend to Entrepreneurs, Hurriyet Reports
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-05-21T06:44:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-21/erdogan-urges-banks-to-lend-to-entrepreneurs-hurriyet-reports.html
Turkish Prime Minister  Recep Tayyip Erdogan  said it’s “unacceptable” that banks are still
hesitating to extend credit to entrepreneurs,  Hurriyet  reported.  Erdogan was speaking at a meeting of the Turkish Union of
Chambers of Commerce yesterday, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
